Author: willieverbefree
Text: You might be underrating and thinking you’re eating more than you really are! Also remember that you won’t eat a meal and gain immediately the next day. I told my doctor I was back to weighing myself everyday and I had ate 2,500 everyday and didn’t gain. She reminded me that weight doesn’t change over night and weighing yourself weekly will give a better indicator of a weight loss trend or weight gain trend. Definitely keep an eye on it.
